{"id":1573,"date":"2018-06-01T09:09:59","date_gmt":"2018-06-01T09:09:59","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/?p=1573"},"modified":"2021-02-27T08:42:52","modified_gmt":"2021-02-27T08:42:52","slug":"xu-huong-mau-sac-trong-thiet-ke-noi-nam-2018","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/xu-huong-mau-sac-trong-thiet-ke-noi-nam-2018\/","title":{"rendered":"Xu h\u01b0\u1edbng m\u00e0u s\u1eafc trong thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t n\u0103m 2018"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">N\u0103m 2018 c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng xu h\u01b0\u1edbng m\u1edbi trong thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i b\u00e0n t\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng m\u00e0u s\u1eafc.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m v\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc, xu h\u01b0\u1edbng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng. N\u0103m 2016 ch\u00fang ta b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u quan t\u00e2m v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u1eabu thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf ph\u00e1 c\u00e1ch&nbsp; v\u1edbi k\u1ebft c\u1ea5u l\u1ea1, \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00e0u s\u1eafc t\u1ea1o \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ea3m x\u00fac m\u1ea1nh. \u0110\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2017 th\u00ec phong c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i t\u1ed1i gi\u1ea3n, tinh t\u1ebf l\u00ean ng\u00f4i; v\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc sang \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2018 phong c\u00e1ch n\u00e0y ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">N\u00f3i m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 ch\u00fang ta chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u xu h\u01b0\u1edbng m\u00e0u s\u1eafc thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf v\u00e0o n\u0103m n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 tinh t\u1ebf m\u00e0 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1574\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/2-1024x640.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"388\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/2-1024x640.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/2-300x188.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/2-768x480.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/2.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" \/><\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">M\u00e0u s\u1eafc n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh hot trend n\u0103m 2018<\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Theo c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 m\u00e0u s\u1eafc hi\u1ec7n nay \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0a chu\u1ed9ng trong thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed3 n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t s\u1ebd v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u gia ch\u1ee7 m\u00ea m\u1ea9n:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">M\u00e0u tr\u1eafng: m\u00e0u tr\u1eafng ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd tr\u1edf n\u00ean l\u1ed7i m\u1ed1t trong thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t. Nh\u01b0ng trong n\u0103m nay, m\u00e0u tr\u1eafng \u0111em l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c tinh t\u1ebf, \u1ea5m \u00e1p ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng g\u1ee3i ra kh\u00f4ng gian c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng suy ngh\u0129 m\u1ec7nh m\u00f4ng, b\u00ed \u1ea9n,\u2026.<\/span><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1575\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/11-1024x640.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"388\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/11-1024x640.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/11-300x188.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/11-768x480.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/11.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" \/><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">M\u00e0u ghi x\u00e1m: B\u1ea1n th\u01b0\u1eddng hay ngh\u0129 m\u00e0u ghi x\u00e1m s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean t\u1ed1i t\u0103m v\u00e0 ch\u1eadt ch\u1ed9i, nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c; b\u1edfi m\u00e0u s\u1eafc n\u00e0y mang \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1ebb \u0111\u1eb9p \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1edd vi\u1ec7c kh\u00e9o l\u00e9o l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t v\u00e0 v\u1eadt d\u1ee5ng trang tr\u00ed ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng.<\/span><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1576\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/pk1a-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"465\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/pk1a-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/pk1a-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/pk1a-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/pk1a-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/pk1a.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" \/><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">M\u00e0u n\u00e2u ( v\u00e2n g\u1ed7):\u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 s\u1eafc m\u00e0u \u1ea5m \u00e1p c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a thu. S\u1eafc m\u00e0u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn n\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0a chu\u1ed9ng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m trong n\u0103m ch\u00fa kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ri\u00eang d\u00e0nh cho m\u00f9a thu. Ng\u00e0y n\u00e0y kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng th\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u1eafc m\u00e0u n\u00e0y v\u00ec n\u00f3 \u0111em t\u1ed